cern.extjfx.chart.plugins

Class AbstractRangeValueIndicator<X,Y>

  • java.lang.Object
    • cern.extjfx.chart.XYChartPlugin<X,Y>
      • cern.extjfx.chart.plugins.AbstractValueIndicator<X,Y>
        • cern.extjfx.chart.plugins.AbstractRangeValueIndicator<X,Y>
  • Type Parameters:
    X - type of X values
    Y - type of Y values
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    XRangeIndicator, YRangeIndicator

    public abstract class AbstractRangeValueIndicator<X,Y>
extends AbstractValueIndicator<X,Y>
    Plugin indicating a value range as a rectangle drawn on the plot area, with an optional text label describing the range.
    Author:
    mhrabia
